utan}} Bhutan\n| East      = {{flagicon|Myanmar}} Myanmar\n| Southeast = {{flagicon|Myanmar}} Myanmar\n| Southwest = {{flagicon|Bangladesh}} Bangladesh\n| West      = [[West Bengal|West Bengal (India)]], {{flagicon|Nepal}} Nepal\n}}\n\n{{North East India|state=collapsed}}\n{{Autonomous Areas of Northeast India}}\n{{Geography of India}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Northeast India| ]]\n[[Category:Regions of India]]\n[[Category:Tourism in North East India]]\n[[Category:Seven Sister States]]\n", "text_old": "{{About|North Eastern Region (NER) of India||Northeast (disambiguation)}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=December 2016}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2016}}\n{{short description|Group of Northeastern Indian states}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->| name                            = Northeast India\n| native_name_lang                = <!-- ISO 639-3 {{lang|ori}} instead --> <!-- ISO 639-2 {{lang|bn}} instead -->\n| settlement_type                 = \n| image_skyline                   = Northeast india.png\n| image_alt                       = \n| image_caption                   = \n| motto                           = \n| image_map                       = Northeast India.svg\n| map_alt                         = Northeast india map.png\n| latd                            = \n| latm                            = \n| lats                            = \n| latNS                           = \n| longd                           = \n| longm                           = \n| longs                           = \n| longEW                          = \n| coordinates_type                = \n| coordinates_display             = \n| coordinates_footnotes           = \n| subdivision_type                = [[Country]]\n| subdivision_name                = {{flag|India}}\n| subdivision_type1               = States\n| subdivision_name1               = {{flatlist|\n* '''[[Arunachal Pradesh]]'''\n* '''[[Assam]]'''\n* '''