us eldii4.jpg|50px]]||[[Clouded leopard]] ''(Neofelis nebulosa)''||[[File:Clouded leopard.jpg|50px]]\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f7f7fe;\"|'''Bird'''|| Hornbill (''[[Buceros bicornis]]'') || [[File:Great-Hornbill.jpg|50px]] || [[White-winged duck]] (''Asarcornis scutulata'') || [[File:White-winged.wood.duck.arp.jpg|50px]]||[[Mrs. Hume's pheasant]] (''Syrmaticus humiae'')||[[File:Syrmaticus humiae.jpg|50px]]|| [[Common hill myna|Hill myna]] ''(Gracula religiosa)''||[[File:Gracula religiosa Deothang Bhutan 1.jpg|50px]]\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f7f7fe;\"|'''Flower'''|| Foxtail orchid (''[[Rhynchostylis retusa]]'') || [[File:Rhynchostylis retusa.JPG|50px]]|| Foxtail orchid (''[[Rhynchostylis retusa]]'') || [[File:Rhynchostylis retusa.JPG|50px]]||[[Siroi lily]] (''Lilium mackliniae'')||[[File:Siroi Lily.jpg|50px]]|| Lady's Slipper Orchid (''[[Paphiopedilum insigne]]'')||[[File:Paphiopedilum insigne Orchi 01.jpg|50px]]\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f7f7fe;\"|'''Tree'''|| [[Hollong]] (''Dipterocarpus macrocarpus'') || [[File:Dipterocarpus macrocarpus Hollong young leafIMG 1920 05.jpg|50px]]|| [[Hollong]] (''Dipterocarpus macrocarpus'') || [[File:Dipterocarpus macrocarpus Hollong young leafIMG 1920 05.jpg|50px]]||Uningthou (''[[Phoebe hainesiana]]'')||[[File:Phoebe hainesiana north Bengal AJTJ.JPG|50px]]|| Gamhar (''[[Gmelina arborea]]'')||[[File:Kamari (Nepalese- \u0915\u093e\u092e\u0930\u0940) (3394494165).jpg|50px]]\n|-\n! || colspan=\"2\"|'''[[Mizoram]]''' || colspan=\"2\"|'''[[Nagaland]]''' || colspan=\"2\"|'''[[Sikkim]]'''||colspan=\"2\"|'''[[Tripura]]'''\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f7f7fe;\"|'''Animal''' ||[[Himalayan serow]]  (''Capricornis thar'')||[[File:Himalayan Serow Pangolakha Wildlife Sanctuary East Sikkim Sikkim India 13.02.2016.jpg|50px]]||Mithun (''[[Bos frontalis]]'') || [[File:Wild Bos frontalis Upparabeeranahalli.jpg|50px]] ||[[Red panda]] (''Ailurus fulgens'')||[[File:RedPandaFullBody.JPG|50px]]||[[Phayre's leaf monkey]] (''Trachypithecus phayrei'')||[[Fi